    package main

    import (
        "fmt"
    )

    func main() {
        bits := []byte{0x01, 0x01, 0x00, 0x01, 0x00, 0x01, 0x01, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00}
        Flags := make([]byte, (len(bits)+7)/8)
        for i := uint32(0); i < uint32(len(bits)); i++ {
            Flags[i/8] |= bits[i] << (i % 8)
        }
        fmt.Println(Flags)
    }
